fno: In the cash market, the Nifty 50 lost 18.10 points or 0.1% to settle at 18,297. The NSE's India VIX, a gauge of market's expectation of volatility over the near term, rose 1.01% to 13.22. Larsen & Toubro (L&T), Asian Paints and Dr. Reddy's Laboratories were the top traded individual stock futures contracts in F&O segment of NSE. The May 2023 F&O contracts will expire on 25 May 2023.
